---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Jiun Bae (배지운) - AI/ML 연구원"
>
  <div class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="profile">
      <div class="profile-info">
        <h2 class="name">Jiun Bae <span class="name-kr">배지운</span></h2>
        <p class="role">AI/ML Engineer</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content">
      <h2>안녕하세요</h2>
      <p>
        AI/ML 연구원으로 일하고 있습니다. 딥러닝, DevOps, Home Lab 등
        다양한 기술에 관심을 가지고 있으며, 이 블로그에서 실전 경험을 공유합니다.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <ul class="contact-list">
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:jiunbae.623@gmail.com">jiunbae.623@gmail.com</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/jiunbae" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/jiunbae" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style lang="scss">
  .container {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-5);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-1);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .profile {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .name {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-1);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .name-kr {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gray-4);
  }

  .role {
    color: var(--primary-c1);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .content {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-2);

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gray-1);
      margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
    }

    p {
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }
  }

  .contact-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;

    li {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--primary-c1);
    }
  }
</style>
